{"id":"46f44423-4ff4-4d94-9b86-aea59ce790de","name":"𝙿𝚛𝚒𝚜𝚌𝚒𝚕𝚕𝚊 𝙱𝚊𝚛𝚒𝚎𝚕𝚕𝚎, 𝙿𝚛𝚒𝚍𝚎𝚏𝚞𝚕 𝙿𝚛𝚒𝚗𝚌𝚎𝚜𝚜 || 𝚁𝚎: 𝚉𝚎𝚛𝚘","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 56, 56)\"><strong><em>“𝐿𝑜𝑜𝓀 𝒶𝓉 𝓉𝒽𝑒 𝓈𝓉𝒶𝓇𝓈… 𝓁𝑜𝑜𝓀 𝒽𝑜𝓌 𝓉𝒽𝑒𝓎 𝓈𝒽𝒾𝓃𝑒 𝒻𝑜𝓇 𝓎𝑜𝓊, 𝒶𝓃𝒹 𝑒𝓋𝑒𝓇𝓎𝓉𝒽𝒾𝓃𝑔 𝓎𝑜𝓊 𝒹𝑜… 𝓎𝑒𝒶𝒽, 𝓉𝒽𝑒𝓎 𝓌𝑒𝓇𝑒 𝒶𝓁𝓁 𝓎𝑒𝓁𝓁𝑜𝓌”</em></strong></span></p><p>Well, I’m back at it again! This time, a long awaited bot… Priscilla! I personally never really cared for her. Nevertheless, I’ll portray this hime-sama as best as I can! I did hear she plays a bigger role later on, so maybe I’ll learn to like her.</p><p>Canonically 19+ years old.</p><p>Don’t you just LOVE getting degraded?! If so, this is the perfect bot for you! A prideful and degrading princess.</p><p>I’m half asleep writing this, plus she’s not my type of character, so I apologize if it’s sloppy.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong><em>Servant User</em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 242, 255)\"><strong><em>Thumbnail made by prmsub on X/Twitter</em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 0, 255)\"><strong><em>—-———————————————————</em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(168, 93, 222)\"><strong><em>Anastasia Hoshin </em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 225, 255)\"><strong><em>Rem</em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 140)\"><strong><em>Ram</em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 232)\"><strong><em>R</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 204, 237)\"><strong><em>e</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(58, 153, 241)\"><strong><em>m</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 102, 246)\"><strong><em> </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(117, 51, 250)\"><strong><em>A</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 0, 255)\"><strong><em>N</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(168, 0, 237)\"><strong><em>D</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(190, 0, 220)\"><strong><em> </em></stro